PrecisAppointment of CLAIRE MORRIS, of Fredericton, New Brunswick, as Deputy Minister of Human Resources Development, to hold office during pleasure; designation of CLAIRE MORRIS as Deputy Minister of Labour; and appointment of CLAIRE MORRIS as a commissioner of the Canada Employment Insurance Commission, who shall be the Chairperson of the Commission.
